Package: CellDeathAnalysis
Title: Comprehensive Analysis of Cell Death Pathways in Gene Expression Data
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Keran", "Sun", , "s1214844197@163.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive R package for analyzing cell death pathway-related 
    gene expression in transcriptomic data. The package provides curated gene 
    sets for 14 types of regulated cell death (including ferroptosis, cuproptosis, 
    disulfidptosis, pyroptosis, necroptosis, apoptosis, autophagy, and more), 
    pathway scoring methods (ssGSEA, GSVA, AUCell), differential expression 
    analysis, enrichment analysis (ORA and GSEA), survival analysis (Kaplan-Meier,
    Cox regression, time-dependent ROC), single-cell analysis, machine learning 
    prediction models, interactive Shiny application, and publication-ready 
    visualizations. Ideal for cancer research, immunology, and cell biology studies.
